    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 8 Creation Points</p><p>Drain: 10 CCD Chakra</p><p></p><p>You have gone beyond the normal limits of Shinobi-Ware. </p><p>Choose Two Scientific Ninja Tools of 4 Creation Point cost or lower. </p><p>You now have permanent access to them and they do not cost Creation Points. </p><p>If they cost Chakra from your CCD you can now pay them with your own chakra. </p><p>Additionally You can spend the CCD Drain of this upgrade to add a spent charge to a Toolkit. </p><p>You can only do this twice per Toolkit.</p>",
